Classic Lemon Raspberry: Frosted with lemon buttercream and topped with a single fresh raspberry.
Glazed Lemon Raspberry Swirl: Frosted with a swirl of lemon glaze, creating a marbled look.
Butterfly Lemon Raspberry: Halve the top of the cupcake, add frosting in the middle, and place the halves on either side like butterfly wings.
Mini Lemon Raspberry Bliss Bites: Mini-sized cupcakes with a dollop of frosting for bite-sized treats.
